His unceasing action toward it will naturally be that of a re-creative influence co- operating with, but not coercing, the progressive action of the self-directing force.

This action would need to be restrained and delicate——as the forces of nature must be restrained toward the crystal that only forms itself in stillness‚ as a nurse is restrained and delicate toward a sleeping babe lest it awake. If this be true, if fatherhood be the best symbol of Omnipotence, I should like in the next chapters to consider what the divine self-revelation to humanity would naturally be.
